                    <div class="col-xl-5 col-lg-6">
                        <div class="tp-pd-2-overview-wrap mr-100">
                            <p>
                                Nexus is a solo-founded digital whiteboard application designed for visual
                                brainstorming and organization. Built with a modern MERN stack (MongoDB,
                                Express, React, Node.js) and TypeScript, it provides an intuitive, infinite
                                canvas inspired by tools like Milanote, following a frontend-first, iterative
                                development strategy.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Key features are already live, including a robust user authentication system
                                with Google OAuth, full cloud persistence for all canvases with an auto-save
                                feature, and advanced canvas tools. The current priority is a full
                                responsiveness overhaul to ensure a seamless mobile experience, with real-time
                                collaboration planned as the next major feature release.
                            </p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Secure User Authentication & Cloud Persistence</li>
                                <li>Advanced Canvas Tools (Bendable Connectors, In-Place Editing, PDF Export)</li>
                                <li>Full Responsiveness & Real-Time Collaboration (In Progress)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
